  <h2>1. What Connect provides</h2>
  <p>
    Connect is a webhook relay service. It receives signed webhook deliveries on a public URL we provide and
    forwards them to your self-hosted ReplayVOD instance over a long-lived WebSocket connection. The relay
    does not parse, log, or persist webhook payload contents beyond a short reconnect buffer (currently five
    minutes). It does not store your video recordings, user accounts, or Twitch credentials. Your videos
    and database remain on the hardware you operate.
  </p>

