    </li>
    <li>
      You will not use Connect to relay traffic that violates applicable law, infringes third-party rights, or
      attempts to circumvent the technical or contractual protections of any platform.
    </li>
    <li>
      You will keep your relay token confidential. Anyone who possesses your token can post events to your
      relay endpoint.
    </li>
  </ul>

